body:
Thank you for reporting this. It is due to my recent change in : https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime/commit/fd334aff44b5e5dfe698716a31808c9d002586b3#diff-2eeaed663bd0d25b7e608891384b7298

We'll update the docker file and fix the issue.

Has this been fixed yet?  or is there any work around in the mean time?
